' Modelo final del Observatorio Económico y de Mercados de Bolivia
' Fuente: elaboración propia basada en SDMX 3.1, GSIM 2.0, UN-NQAF e INE Bolivia.
' Archivo autónomo: no requiere includes externos.

@startuml
title Estado — data_issue
skinparam shadowing false
[*] --> OPEN
OPEN --> TRIAGED : classify
TRIAGED --> IN_CORRECTION : assign
TRIAGED --> DISMISSED : falsePositive / acceptedException
IN_CORRECTION --> RESOLVED : correctionApplied
RESOLVED --> VERIFIED : qualityRecheckPassed
RESOLVED --> IN_CORRECTION : recheckFailed
VERIFIED --> CLOSED : close
CLOSED --> REOPENED : newEvidence
REOPENED --> TRIAGED
DISMISSED --> [*]
CLOSED --> [*]
@enduml
